apt update
apt install docker.io
apt install docker-compose
mkdir hashtopolis
cd hashtopolis
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hashtopolis/server/master/docker-compose.yml
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/hashtopolis/server/master/env.example -O .env
docker-compose up -d
http://ip:8080

# **Hashtopolis Agent** After that, you need to download the hashtopolis.zip and run this command "python hashtopolis.zip cmd/powershell", install all the necessary libraries, specify "url", "token", "voucher", and you're done.
